Assignment 2: HA and Robust Applications

To package and run the application:

1. Unzip the tar file containing source code and Docker file
2. Open terminal and access the directory of the unzipped file (now a folder)
3. Launch the Docker compose: "docker-compose up"
4. Invoke the API through Postman, Insomnia or the URL
* http://localhost:5001/dishes and http://localhost:5001/meals to send all requests to the Meals Service
* http://localhost:5002/diets to send all requests to the Diets Service
* http://localhost:80/dishes, /meals, /diets to send GET requests to the Meals and Diets Service
